messages: Google LLC[5] is an American multinational technology company that specializes in Internet-related services and products, which include online advertising technologies, search engine, cloud computing, software, and hardware. It is considered one of the Big Four of technology (alternatively "Four Horsemen") along with Amazon, Apple and Facebook.
